window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The world is ablaze with great deeds and incredible people.</b></p> <p>The King of Duels' battle with the King of Destruction is still ringing across the continent of Chandrar, but more adventures are taking place at sea with Niers' students and on Izril's shores.</p> <p>The Horns have arrived in Invrisil at last, and they will soon find out that Gold-rankers they might be, that doesn't guarantee instantaneous respect from other high-level teams. However, a certain [Lady] has also begun her final journey...once again, attention and excitement swing back to The Wandering Inn thanks to a certain magic door!</p> <p>It is a time of fire and men with hats and fantastic momentsâ€”and dark ones too, sometimes. However, even the meagerest spark can turn into a roaring flame.</p> <p>Book 17 of The Wandering Inn contains raiders, assassins, magical flames, hats, and...football? Or is it soccer?</p>"; 
